{
  "schema": {
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
      "id": {"type": "number"},
      "name": {"type": "string"}
    },
    "required": ["id", "name"]
  },
  "data": {
    "id": 1,
    "name": "test"
  },
  "options": {}
}
</tool_call>

Since both the network fetch and validation steps failed, I'll try the final step in the original plan - data parsing - using the data_processing_parser tool with some sample data.

